1. First, use the 'Recruitment Metrics' tool to retrieve the current October 2025 hiring standards and evaluation framework
2. Analyze the candidate's resume against the JOB DETAILS provided above using the recruitment metrics standards
3. Provide a comprehensive, enterprise-grade evaluation

